49, \"to\": 1060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What do we want?\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An OLYMPIC WAGE!\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An OLYMPIC WAGE\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When do we want it?\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NOW!#TourismWorkersRisingLAmotion aims to raise the wage for over 36,000 tourism workers to $25/hour immediately, $30/hour by the 2028 Olympics, and give workers access to quality health care.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NOW!#TourismWorkersRisingLAmotion\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"the wage\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"over 36,000 tourism workers\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"$25/hour\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2028 Olympics\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"quality health care\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2764\\ufe0f\\ud83d\\udc9cpic.twitter.com/y8hiZr2TaT 'We need this' As the city's tourism industrybounces back to near pre-pandemic levels, labor advocates say the Olympics could be a boon to corporations, while a bane to the low-wage workers who keep LAX, hotels and the rest of the city's tourism engine running smoothly.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u2764\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's tourism\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"pre-pandemic levels\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"labor advocates\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"a boon\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"corporations\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"a bane\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"the low-wage workers\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"LAX\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"hotels\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's tourism engine\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's appalling to think that while the tourism industry has its future growth secured, our families are fighting to keep a roof over their heads,\\\" Councilmember Curren Price said during the rally.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tourism industry\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"its future growth\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"our families\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"a roof\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"their heads\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"Councilmember Curren Price\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"the rally\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Price co-wrote a motion in April 2023 proposing the pay increases, and a city report was commissioned later that year to analyze the economic impact of raising wages.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a motion\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"the pay increases\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"a city report\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"the economic impact\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"wages\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is expected to be released within two weeks, said Chief Legislative Analyst Sharon Tso.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc